node.text: As a victim of severe domestic violence and a single mother raising two small boys alone I thought it was important to show them that one can overcome all the pain and suffering and rise above to be overwhelmingly powerful. Thank you @royalpersonaltraining @shayansafai87 @benny_wilk for all your love, encouragement and support 💕🙏
